<h1><i class="fa fa-image"></i>Changing Your Background</h1>

<ol class="breadcrumb">
	<li><a href="#help"><i class="fa fa-question-circle"></i>Help</a></li>
	<li><a href="#help/customizing-environment"><i class="fa fa-paint-brush"></i>Customizing Your Environment</a></li>
	<li><i class="fa fa-image"></i>Changing Your Background</li>
</ol>

<div class="content">
	<p>The background provides an effective way to personalize your user experience.  <%= application.name %> allows to to change the background color and image or pattern to suit your liking. </p>

	<ol>
		<li>
			<h2><i class="fa fa-paint-brush"></i>Background Settings</h2>
			<p>The <a href="#help/getting-started/using-desktop">Desktop</a> background is controlled through the <a href="#apps/theme-manager">Theme Manager</a> app. To view and change the <a href="#help/getting-started/using-desktop">Desktop</a> background, click on the second tab, labelled "Background". </p>

			<div class="figure">
				<a href="images/help/customizing-environment/changing-background/background-settings.png" target="_blank" class="lightbox" title='"Background" Tab on the Theme Manager App'><img class="dialog" src="images/help/customizing-environment/changing-background/background-settings.png" /></a>
				<div class="caption">"Background" Tab on the Theme Manager App</div>
			</div>
		</li>

		<li>
			<h2><i class="fa fa-image"></i>Background Image</h2>
			<p>To select a background image, click the "Select" button.  This will bring up a dialog box that allows you to select a background image.  A variety of background images in various categories are provided for you to choose from. </p>

			<div class="figure">
				<a href="images/help/customizing-environment/changing-background/select-background-image-dialog.png" target="_blank" class="lightbox" title="Select Background Image Dialog"><img class="dialog" src="images/help/customizing-environment/changing-background/select-background-image-dialog.png" /></a>
				<div class="caption">Select Background Image Dialog</div>
			</div>

			<p>Below are some examples of standard background images that have been provided for you: </p>

			<div class="figure row">
				<div class="figure col-sm-6">
					<a href="images/help/customizing-environment/changing-background/background-image.png" target="_blank" class="lightbox" title="Background Image" rel="group1"><img src="images/help/customizing-environment/changing-background/background-image.png" /></a>
					<div class="caption">Background Image</div>
				</div>
				<div class="figure col-sm-6">
					<a href="images/help/customizing-environment/changing-background/background-gradient.png" target="_blank" class="lightbox" title="Background Gradient" rel="group1"><img src="images/help/customizing-environment/changing-background/background-gradient.png" /></a>
					<div class="caption">Background Gradient</div>
				</div>
				<div class="figure col-sm-6">
					<a href="images/help/customizing-environment/changing-background/background-material.png" target="_blank" class="lightbox" title="Background Material" rel="group1"><img src="images/help/customizing-environment/changing-background/background-material.png" /></a>
					<div class="caption">Background Material</div>
				</div>
				<div class="figure col-sm-6">
					<a href="images/help/customizing-environment/changing-background/background-pattern.png" target="_blank" class="lightbox" title="Background Pattern" rel="group1"><img src="images/help/customizing-environment/changing-background/background-pattern.png" /></a>
					<div class="caption">Background Pattern</div>
				</div>
			</div>

			<div class="tip well">
				<h3><span class="icon"><i class="fa fa-lightbulb"></i></span>Tip</h3><p>If you want to select one of your own images rather than the ones that have been provided, double-click on the "Home" or "Pictures" folders in the Favorites sidebar.</p>
			</div>
		</li>

		<li>
			<h2><i class="fa fa-arrows-alt"></i>Background Size</h2>
			<p>When you select a background image, you will be given the option to set the image size. The size and position of the background image in relation to the <a href="#help/getting-started/using-desktop">Desktop</a> area will be shown in the thumbnail preview. </p>

			<div class="figure">
				<a href="images/help/customizing-environment/changing-background/background-image-settings.png" target="_blank" class="lightbox" title="Background Image Size Settings"><img class="dialog" src="images/help/customizing-environment/changing-background/background-image-settings.png" /></a>
				<div class="caption">Background Image Size Settings</div>
			</div>

			<ul>
				<li><label>Cover</label><br>
				The background image covers the <a href="#help/getting-started/using-desktop">Desktop</a>.  This is the most common setting to use.</li>
				<li><label>Contain</label><br>
				The background image is contained in the <a href="#help/getting-started/using-desktop">Desktop</a>.  If the aspect ratios do not match, then the background color will be shown in the areas that the background image does not cover.</li>
				<li><label>Center</label><br>
				The background image is centered in the <a href="#help/getting-started/using-desktop">Desktop</a>.  If the background image is smaller than the <a href="#help/getting-started/using-desktop">Desktop</a>, then the background color will be shown in the areas that the background image does not cover. </li>
				<li><label>Tile</label><br>
				The background image will repeat across the <a href="#help/getting-started/using-desktop">Desktop</a>.</li>
			</ul>

			<div class="figure row">
				<div class="figure col-sm-6">
					<a href="images/help/customizing-environment/changing-background/background-image-cover.png" target="_blank" class="lightbox" title="Cover Background Image" rel="group2"><img src="images/help/customizing-environment/changing-background/background-image-cover.png" /></a>
					<div class="caption">Cover Background Image</div>
				</div>
				<div class="figure col-sm-6">
					<a href="images/help/customizing-environment/changing-background/background-image-contain.png" target="_blank" class="lightbox" title="Contain Background Image" rel="group2"><img src="images/help/customizing-environment/changing-background/background-image-contain.png" /></a>
					<div class="caption">Contain Background Image</div>
				</div>
				<div class="figure col-sm-6">
					<a href="images/help/customizing-environment/changing-background/background-image-center.png" target="_blank" class="lightbox" title="Center Background Image" rel="group2"><img src="images/help/customizing-environment/changing-background/background-image-center.png" /></a>
					<div class="caption">Center Background Image</div>
				</div>
				<div class="figure col-sm-6">
					<a href="images/help/customizing-environment/changing-background/background-image-tiled.png" target="_blank" class="lightbox" title="Tile Background Image" rel="group2"><img src="images/help/customizing-environment/changing-background/background-image-tiled.png" /></a>
					<div class="caption">Tile Background Image</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</li>

		<li>
			<h2><i class="fa fa-th"></i>Tiling Backgrounds</h2>
			<p>When you select a background size of "Tile", then the background image will be repeated across the <a href="#help/getting-started/using-desktop">Desktop</a>.  You can control the number of repeats using the repeat slider control. </p>

			<div class="figure">
				<a href="images/help/customizing-environment/changing-background/background-tiling-settings.png" target="_blank" class="lightbox" title="Background Tiling Settings"><img class="dialog" src="images/help/customizing-environment/changing-background/background-tiling-settings.png" /></a>
				<div class="caption">Background Tiling Settings</div>
			</div>

			<div class="figure row">
				<div class="figure col-sm-6">
					<a href="images/help/customizing-environment/changing-background/background-repeat-5x.png" target="_blank" class="lightbox" title="Background Repeat 5x" rel="group3"><img src="images/help/customizing-environment/changing-background/background-repeat-5x.png" /></a>
					<div class="caption">Background Repeat 5x</div>
				</div>
				<div class="figure col-sm-6">
					<a href="images/help/customizing-environment/changing-background/background-repeat-10x.png" target="_blank" class="lightbox" title="Background Repeat 10x" rel="group3"><img src="images/help/customizing-environment/changing-background/background-repeat-10x.png" /></a>
					<div class="caption">Background Repeat 10x</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</li>

		<li>
			<h2><i class="fa fa-paint-brush"></i>Background</h2>
			<p>If you are a minimalist, you can set also the background to a single, uniform color. To do so, click the "Clear" button to clear any previously set background image, then click the checkbox labelled "Color". <p>

			<div class="figure">
				<a href="images/help/customizing-environment/changing-background/background-color-settings.png" target="_blank" class="lightbox" title="Setting Background"><img class="dialog" src="images/help/customizing-environment/changing-background/background-color-settings.png" /></a>
				<div class="caption">Setting Background</div>
			</div>

			<p>When you click the color checkbox, a color picker will appear that allows you to select a color of your liking.  As you change the color, the <a href="#help/getting-started/using-desktop">Desktop</a> will update to show you the new color. </p>

			<div class="figure">
				<a href="images/help/customizing-environment/changing-background/color-picker.png" target="_blank" class="lightbox" title="Color Picker"><img src="images/help/customizing-environment/changing-background/color-picker.png" /></a>
				<div class="caption">Color Picker</div>
			</div>

			<div class="tip well">
				<h3><span class="icon"><i class="fa fa-lightbulb"></i></span>Tip</h3><p>Note that the appearance of the color picker may vary depending on your web browser and operating system. </p>
			</div>
		</li>
	</ol>
</div>